column2: SELECT TOP #  s.specObjID,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.objid,s.ra,s.dec,s.mag_#, s.mag_#, s.mag_#,  s.specClass, s.z,  s.plate, s.mjd, f.mjd, s.fiberid, s.objTypeName, s.objType FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN Field AS f ON f.fieldid = p.fieldid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #
